{"chapter":241,"line_start":42,"line_end":42,"text":"项少龙施展擒拿手法，一把扭着其中一名御者的手腕"}]},{"id":"tech_rou_dao_shen_fa","name":"柔道身法","type":"defense","description":"借力打力的近身摔法，利用对手冲力将其摔过头顶","source_skill":null,"source_refs":[{"chapter":241,"line_start":38,"line_end":38,"text":"再使了一下柔道的身法，扭身把后面的人摔过头顶"}]}],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[{"id":"item_xue_lang_bao_jian","name":"血浪宝剑","type":"weapon","owner":"char_xiang_shao_long","one_line":"项少龙随身宝剑，剑法出神入化","description":"项少龙的随身佩剑，剑身锋利无比，出鞘时化作漫天剑影，削铁如泥","effects":["伤害","特殊"],"origin":"不详","rarity":"上乘佳品","related_characters":["char_xiang_shao_long"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[241],"source_refs":[{"chapter":241,"line_start":58,"line_end":60,"text":"血浪宝剑离鞘而出，化作漫天剑影"}]},{"id":"item_bi_shou","name":"匕首","type":"weapon","owner":"char_gu_ming","one_line":"谷明随身携带的短兵器","description":"谷明从怀中拔出的近身短兵器，用于偷袭和近战，被项少龙击落后坠地","effects":["伤害"],"origin":"不详","rarity":"寻常凡品","related_characters":["char_gu_ming"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[241],"source_refs":[{"chapter":241,"line_start":48,"line_end":50,"text":"由怀里拔出匕首，当胸搠至"}]}]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":96,"line_end":195,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_dong_shu_zhen","speaker_name":"董淑贞","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"沈良！这是什么一回事，自你来后，屡生事端，可知我团严禁私斗？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":241,"line_start":102,"line_end":104},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":null,"text":"若想知道是怎样一回事，何不问问小玲姊，她是策划的人，自然知道得比我更清楚。","tone":"淡然","chapter":241,"line_start":110,"line_end":112},{"speaker":"char_sha_li","speaker_name":"沙立","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"沈良你是什么身份，竟没上没下的，还不给我跪下。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":241,"line_start":114,"line_end":116},{"speaker":"char_feng_fei","speaker_name":"凤菲","listener":null,"text":"给我住嘴！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":241,"line_start":122,"line_end":122},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":null,"text":"士可杀，不可辱，男儿膝下有黄金，若要我为沙立这种卑鄙小人折腰，那可要杀了我才办得到。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":241,"line_start":126,"line_end":128},{"speaker":"char_sha_li","speaker_name":"沙立","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"让我来取你这大胆奴才的狗命。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":241,"line_start":130,"line_end":132},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_sha_li","text":"你若是我十招之敌，我便向你叩十个响头。","tone":"调侃","chapter":241,"line_start":134,"line_end":134},{"speaker":"char_zhang_quan","speaker_name":"张泉","listener":"char_sha_li","text":"沙副管事若有真本领，我张泉乐于一开眼界。","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":241,"line_start":138,"line_end":138},{"speaker":"char_yun_niang","speaker_name":"云娘","listener":null,"text":"这么吵吵闹闹的，成什么体统，更不能解决事情。","tone":"无奈","chapter":241,"line_start":140,"line_end":142},{"speaker":"char_feng_fei","speaker_name":"凤菲","listener":"char_wu_xun","text":"好了！让我们平心静气来把事情弄清楚，巫循你乃家将之首，告诉我这是什么一回事？","tone":"温柔","chapter":241,"line_start":146,"line_end":148},{"speaker":"char_gu_ming","speaker_name":"谷明","listener":null,"text":"这事是由沈良惹起，我们一众兄弟在舱内耍乐，沈良却……","tone":"陈述","chapter":241,"line_start":152,"line_end":153},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ping_er","speaker_name":"小屏儿","listener":"char_gu_ming","text":"小姐问的是巫循，怎到你这奴才插嘴？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":241,"line_start":154,"line_end":156},{"speaker":"char_wu_xun","speaker_name":"巫循","listener":null,"text":"是的，沈良闯进来没头没脑的对我们拳打脚踢，就是这样子。","tone":"颤声","chapter":241,"line_start":160,"line_end":162},{"speaker":"char_zhang_quan","speaker_name":"张泉","listener":"char_wu_xun","text":"他怎会知你们躲在哪个舱房内耍乐呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":241,"line_start":164,"line_end":164},{"speaker":"char_sha_li","speaker_name":"沙立","listener":"char_zhang_quan","text":"大管事是否要纵容凶徒？现在摆明沈良是行凶伤人，只看现在他大胆无礼的样子，当知此人的狂妄。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":241,"line_start":168,"line_end":170},{"speaker":"char_dong_shu_zhen","speaker_name":"董淑贞","listener":null,"text":"你们给我先静下来。","tone":"严肃","chapter":241,"line_start":172,"line_end":172},{"speaker":"char_dong_shu_zhen","speaker_name":"董淑贞","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"沈良你有什么话说？","tone":"疑问","chapter":241,"line_start":174,"line_end":174},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_dong_shu_zhen","text":"我没有话好说，只要二小姐一句话，我便自行离去，把事情了结。","tone":"淡然","chapter":241,"line_start":176,"line_end":178},{"speaker":"char_zhang_quan","speaker_name":"张泉","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"你怎可全不辩白而退出？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":241,"line_start":180,"line_end":180},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_zhang_quan","text":"张爷肯聘用我，亦是出自私心，现在我沈良省悟了，再不会被你利用，还留在这里干啥？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":241,"line_start":182,"line_end":184},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ling_zi","speaker_name":"小玲姊","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"你这以下犯上的奴才，打伤了人，走得那么容易吗？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":241,"line_start":188,"line_end":190},{"speaker":"char_dong_shu_zhen","speaker_name":"董淑贞","listener":"char_xiao_ling_zi","text":"小玲住嘴！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":241,"line_start":192,"line_end":192}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_kun_shan","name":"昆山","alias":[],"identity":"歌舞姬团家将","faction":"歌舞姬团","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"歌舞姬团家将之一，列队旁观审判","personality":{"traits":["沉默","忠诚","服从","谨慎","稳重"],"speech_style":"沉默寡言","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[241],"source_refs":[{"chapter":241,"line_start":98,"line_end":98,"text":"至于昆山等一众家将"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":196,"line_end":264,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_dong_shu_zhen","speaker_name":"董淑贞","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"现在已非谁动手伤人的问题，而是沈良你目无尊卑的态度。","tone":"严肃","chapter":241,"line_start":202,"line_end":204},{"speaker":"char_dong_shu_zhen","speaker_name":"董淑贞","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"你显然并非平凡之辈，但这只是一个歌舞姬团，容纳不下你这种人，所以……","tone":"认真","chapter":241,"line_start":206,"line_end":206},{"speaker":"char_feng_fei","speaker_name":"凤菲","listener":null,"text":"且慢！","tone":"严肃","chapter":241,"line_start":208,"line_end":208},{"speaker":"char_feng_fei","speaker_name":"凤菲","listener":null,"text":"想不到我们小小一个歌舞姬团，竟也会生出这么多事端。\n\n这事罪不在沈良，而在于管事的人。一向以来，我都忍着不出声，岂知现在你们变本加厉，我再不能不说话。","tone":"无奈","chapter":241,"line_start":216,"line_end":220},{"speaker":"char_feng_fei","speaker_name":"凤菲","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"沈良你放心为我驾车，以后若有任何人敢惹你，可以直接向我报告。","tone":"温柔","chapter":241,"line_start":226,"line_end":228},{"speaker":"char_zhang_quan","speaker_name":"张泉","listener":null,"text":"小人知罪！小人知罪！","tone":"恐惧","chapter":241,"line_start":240,"line_end":241},{"speaker":"char_sha_li","speaker_name":"沙立","listener":"char_feng_fei","text":"大小姐，事发时小人并不在船上……","tone":"陈述","chapter":241,"line_start":242,"line_end":242},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ling_zi","speaker_name":"小玲姊","listener":"char_sha_li","text":"你竟敢说这种话？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":241,"line_start":244,"line_end":244},{"speaker":"char_dong_shu_zhen","speaker_name":"董淑贞","listener":"char_xiao_ling_zi","text":"小玲跪下，由今天起，我再不用你伺候！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":241,"line_start":246,"line_end":246},{"speaker":"char_feng_fei","speaker_name":"凤菲","listener":"char_sha_li","text":"待会儿船泊码头，沙立你立即给我滚得远远的，否则休怪我辣手无情。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":241,"line_start":250,"line_end":252},{"speaker":"char_feng_fei","speaker_name":"凤菲","listener":"char_zhang_quan","text":"念在你跟了我这么多年，亦肯知机认错，便让你降级为副管事，有关钱银往来的事，暂改由云娘负责。\n\n至于谷明等犯事者，一律扣起这个月的工钱，异议者立即逐走。","tone":"严肃","chapter":241,"line_start":254,"line_end":258}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_zhang_quan","updates":{"rank":"登堂入室","source_refs":[{"chapter":241,"line_start":254,"line_end":254,"text":"便让你降级为副管事"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_feng_fei","type":"主仆","intensity":40,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"被降级"}]},{"id":"char_sha_li","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":241,"line_start":250,"line_end":252,"text":"沙立你立即给我滚得远远的"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_feng_fei","type":"宿敌","intensity":90,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"被驱逐"}]},{"id":"char_xiao_ling_zi","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":241,"line_start":246,"line_end":246,"text":"由今天起，我再不用你伺候"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_dong_shu_zhen","type":"主仆","intensity":30,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"被辞退"}]}]}
